# Any of several perennial [[grass]]es, of genus ''[[Miscanthus]]'', native to [[subtropical]] and [[tropical]] regions of [[Africa]] and southern [[Asia]], which is cultivated as an [[ornamental]] plant and is being used as a source of [[biomass]] for the production of [[biofuel]].